data.description: Come be the lucky homeowner that gets to enjoy this beautiful home that sits on over 1/2 an acre, being the largest in the neighborhood. Open split floor plan, 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and vaulted ceilings. The garage is vented with heat and air; the room in the garage can be used for an office, workout room, etc. and is not included in home square footage. Enjoy the huge deck overlooking the backyard and shared pond. New shingles in 2020.
